  <slide>
    <title>Questions to ask vendors</title>
    <contents>
      <ul>
        <li>Does the company have a VPAT or other documentation on the accessibility of the product?</li>
        <li>Who at the company is responsible for the accessibility of the product?</li>
        <li>How does the company verify the accessibility of the product?</li>
        <li>What assistive technologies and versions does the company use to test accessibility?</li>
        <li>Does the company include people with disabilities in user testing?</li>
      </ul>
    </contents>
  </slide>
  
